Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will blood flow through this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.99,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(360,340)}A Child's View
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:42.64,DVD Titles2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\i1\an8}"The falling deaths of children...\NIs it suicide or murder?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:48.73,DVD Titles2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\i1\an8}"Was it just dangerous child's play?\NOr is this the next victim!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:55.11,DVD Titles2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\i1\an8}"A fifth victim... Entry Restrictions to\NBuilding Rooftops to be Reinforced!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.03,Names2,,0,0,40,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}Ralph Ludwich Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened on the roof back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do? Could you tell\Nme anything you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out, Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't hit the first floor awning and landed\Nin the bushes, you might be dead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the doctor like a good boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so that stupid things like this won't keep on happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... If he died, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to counsel the boy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... I know, but Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk outside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, be a good boy and stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wander into the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he your grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just watching over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does what hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injuries... Your bandaged injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you scared when you fell from the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some shoes in that bag. Get them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of them getting mad at me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you make it back, go outside."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"The world will change."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that the world changed. I'm the one who changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the world is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him, he's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't want to die! Save me!"\NIs that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer your question from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me if I was scared when I fell from the roof, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't be afraid, since I was just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing? People have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun. It was just play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us stood on an abandoned building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd close our eyes and walk towards\Neach other, one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you fell or whatever happened,\Nif you could survive, you'd win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like making a wager with fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who survives was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who survives can play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Play? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun. Only the ones chosen\Nby fate can keep on playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand after you\Nsee it, you truly are a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you aren't thinking of going up to the roof, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The superior people will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like "that person."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "that person?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who taught me this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The friend of us superior children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon. You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to understand. So just come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who beat you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be on their side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they did that to you, do you still\Nintend to be buried in this stupid world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. Take a look for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the view from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up. What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, close your eyes, and try walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand everything you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the world was pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the future was pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite food?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ate some delicious sausage, but\Nif I died, I'd never get to eat it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Scaredy cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I like soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I died, I wouldn't kick a ball ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Dr. Reichwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His secretary, Ms. Mereth, is kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I died, I'd never see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There will always be things to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he said to become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Tenma taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I died, I'd never see Tenma again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Carefully, bend your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is playing even better games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan said that he's going to be killed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's going to be shot by a Japanese man real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed my eyes and walked on the edge of the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I walked up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I opened my eyes, Joachim, who should\Nhave been right in front of me, was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it. I saw the instant when someone\Ndies with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People really die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this kid. It's like he doesn't\Neven know what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's alive, but when I think of\Nhow Joachim's parents must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please talk some sense into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he'd listen to whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She annoys me like that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't let me out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,TV and comics are off-limits for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come bring you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't have comics, then how about a picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture book? That sounds boring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This great game you told me about... have you played it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you might be shot soon, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When is that Japanese person going to shoot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Herman Hesse's {\i1}Der Steppenwolf{\i0}, first edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoffman's {\i1}Nachtstucke{\i0}, first edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an entire collection of Goethe's poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book collection big enough to make even me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the head librarian at Munich University's\NFredrich Emannuel Library, dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it this far in life with self-study.\NI didn't go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I'd just read books\Nto learn, and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To have such a large collection of\Nbooks donated to my library, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough words to thank you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyesight is getting worse, so soon\NI won't be able to read them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'd do more good in the hands of students\Nrather than being allowed to sleep here in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, many of the books are valuable, but they\Nshould be accessible to normal people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already set aside a place for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a ceremony, so if\Nyou could please speak at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about security?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Mr. Schubert has taken control of his\Ncompanies, I've been worried about his safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure that the invited guests\Nare checked out thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl and Johan, who suggested that\NI donate these books, will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Head Librarian, Gerhmann.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:01.54,Names2,,0,0,40,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}Munich University Library
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the room where we are going to\Nput the books that Mr. Schubert is donating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular visitors are not able to come back this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably have never been here either, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature and humidity are at optimum levels for storage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course, this place is safe from fire or theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a collection of great books!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly a treasure of humanity.\NDon't you think so, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A treasure of humanity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll hold the donation ceremony in this center hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as your butler said, the security will be very tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like Mr. Schubert to feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Dad will love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm looking for a nice picture book for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a nice picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a little too adult for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So your friend isn't a grown-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit clumsy, so I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the book I was going to suggest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it has nice pictures. I wonder whose book that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Emil Scherbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The publisher is Moravia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That publisher is located in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of good picture book\Nartists in the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never heard of Scherbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He must not be very famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone come now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer is so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:41.32,DVD Titles2,,0,0,20,,{\fs24\fad(500,0)\an8\b0}"Announcing Mr. Hans Georg Schubert's Book\NCollection Donation Ceremony and Speech."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:43.49,ED - TL,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Gazing at what is known now in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:23:00.89,ED - TL,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Your eyes believe in kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:25.97,ED - TL,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:34.45,ED - TL,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it home... to your land of purity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.49,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}At the Edge of Darkness
